high_descs: Walk to the table ahead.
Grab the knife that's under the leftmost bread.
Turn right and walk towards the counter to the left of the sink.
Slice up the potato.
Put the knife down.
Grab one potato slice.
Turn left and face the microwave.
Heat the potato slice for 2 seconds in the microwave.
Turn left to reach the fridge.
Place the slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place the heated potato slice in the fridge.

high_descs: Go forward to the brown table.
Take the yellow handle knife under the loaf of bread on the left.
Turn right, go to the counter to the right of the sink.
Cut the potato on the counter into slices.
Put the knife on the counter.
Take a slice of potato from the counter.
Turn left towards the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave, turn on the microwave, take the potato from the microwave.
Turn around, go to the refrigerator in the corner of the room to the left.
Put the potato on the shelf below the glass in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn left, turn right, go to table
Grab yellow handled knife on table
Take right, go to edge of counter
Cut open potato on counter
Slice potato on counter
pick up slice of potato, set down knife on counter
Turn around, walk to the counter on right
Place potato slice in microwave, cook, remove from microwave
Go to left, go to wall, take left to fridge
Place potato slice in fridge
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato, cook it, cool it in fridge.
